1
00:00:03,199 --> 00:00:08,686
Rādhā-ruchi-ruchavṛtam 
guru-rūpa harim gauram:

2
00:00:08,686 --> 00:00:12,979
when Kṛṣṇa takes the guru-rūpa,
the form of guru,

3
00:00:13,069 --> 00:00:16,089
Rādhā-ruchi—He becomes Gaurāṅga.

4
00:00:16,089 --> 00:00:18,823
[Heart and Halo]

5
00:00:19,662 --> 00:00:22,778
It’s Kṛṣṇa enveloped, under the influence,

6
00:00:22,778 --> 00:00:25,345
of the heart and halo of Śrīmati Rādhārāṇī.

7
00:00:25,345 --> 00:00:31,199
Then, sva-bhaktebhyaḥ śuddhasṁ
nija-bhajana-mudrām upadiśan;
[Chaitanyastakam 1.1]

8
00:00:31,199 --> 00:00:36,042
then He’s teaching what is Kṛṣṇa
consciousness.

9
00:00:36,042 --> 00:00:38,612
It’s very interesting

10
00:00:38,612 --> 00:00:41,320
because we take it that guru
is the functioning principle

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,821
of Divinity revealing Himself,

12
00:00:43,821 --> 00:00:47,142
but when He wants to teach devotion,

13
00:00:47,142 --> 00:00:50,633
He takes the position of Mahāprabhu;

14
00:00:50,633 --> 00:00:56,690
has to be under the influence
of Śrīmati Rādhārāṇī

15
00:00:57,277 --> 00:01:01,731
to give a full, proper conception of Kṛṣṇa,

16
00:01:03,698 --> 00:01:06,352
a devotional conception of Kṛṣṇa.
 

17
00:01:06,352 --> 00:01:10,055
This is why Mahāprabhu
descended into the world—

18
00:01:10,055 --> 00:01:14,567
to broadcast the glories of Rādhārāṇī.

19
00:01:15,508 --> 00:01:20,250
Everyone already knows 
so much about Kṛṣṇa,

20
00:01:20,654 --> 00:01:22,976
or thinks they do.

21
00:01:23,793 --> 00:01:30,068
But He’s come to broadcast the greatness
of Śrī Rādhā mahimā—

22
00:01:30,068 --> 00:01:34,089
Her glories; prema-rasa-sīmā—

23
00:01:34,089 --> 00:01:39,367
and what is the highest type of Kṛṣṇa-prema.
That He wants to be known.

24
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:45,230
Kṛṣṇa descends as Mahāprabhu
to reveal that in the world.

25
00:01:45,638 --> 00:01:49,242
And to bring others in connection
with that divine substance.

26
00:01:49,242 --> 00:01:52,905
anarpita-charīṁ chirāt karuṇayāvatīrṇaḥ kalau

27
00:01:52,905 --> 00:01:57,393
samarpayitum unnatojjvala-rasāṁ sva-bhakti-śriyam
[CС: Ādi, 1.4]

